          <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-2">Eliud Wambua</h1>
            <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold">Technology innovator & software developer</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted" style="max-width:70ch">I build practical technology solutions across web, AI, and IoT that focus on health, sustainability, and youth empowerment. Open to research collaborations, internships, and forward-thinking tech opportunities.</p>
            <p class="mt-3"><a href="#projects" class="btn btn-success btn-lg me-2">See projects</a><a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Contact</a></p>
