          <h3 class="h4">Profession summary</h3>
          <p>Technology innovator with solid experience in software programming, research, and emerging technologies. Success track record in executing technology-driven projects that intersect health, sustainability, and youth empowerment. Experience in web application development, Internet of Things (IoT) platforms, and artificial intelligence (AI) solutions, with emphasis on practical solutions and concrete outcomes.</p>

          <h4 class="mt-3">Contact</h4>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:meliudwambua@gmail.com">meliudwambua@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +254 746 699 187</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="mt-3">Education</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Kenya Methodist University (2022 – 2025) — Bachelor of Science in Business Information Technology</li>
            <li>Modcom Institute of Technology (04/2022 - 08/2022) — Software Development</li>
            <li>AIC Chebisaas Boys’ High School (2018 – 2022) — KCSE</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="mt-3">Partnerships & community involvement</h4>
          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 align-items-center">
